    <item>
      <title>受关税风险影响，花旗将标普 500 指数的悲观预测下调至 5,100 点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/citi-has-s-p-500-bear-case-scenario-of-5-100-on-tariff-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗银行全球研究主管露西·鲍德温 (Lucy Baldwin) 表示，今年是“选股的好年头”，因为她认为特朗普总统大规模征收关税可能会导致 2025 年企业盈利增长减半。鲍德温敦促客户考虑“广泛分散投资，不要过度集中在美国市场或任何特定行业”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/citi-has-s-p-500-bear-case-scenario-of-5-100-on-tariff-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:51:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟誓言采取贸易报复措施 图斯克抨击“愚蠢的关税战”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/eu-leaders-say-they-ll-react-to-trump-s-stupid-tariff-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普总统兑现最近的威胁，欧洲有能力对美国的新关税作出反应，并与众多欧洲领导人一起承诺在必要时采取报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/eu-leaders-say-they-ll-react-to-trump-s-stupid-tariff-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:44:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区通胀意外加速，支持欧洲央行谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/euro-zone-inflation-unexpectedly-quickens-backing-ecb-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区通胀意外加速，支持欧洲央行谨慎降低利率，而疲软的经济则面临来自美国日益加剧的贸易威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/euro-zone-inflation-unexpectedly-quickens-backing-ecb-caution</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
