    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税措施后投资者纷纷涌向美元避险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/wall-street-backs-the-dollar-s-wild-rally-to-gather-steam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团和摩根大通等华尔街银行认为，即使在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税举措导致美元飙升之后，购买美元仍然可以赚到很多钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/wall-street-backs-the-dollar-s-wild-rally-to-gather-steam</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普启动关税措施 墨西哥比索领跌新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexican-peso-rand-lead-em-currency-selloff-on-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对美国一些最大的贸易伙伴征收关税后，新兴市场货币周一兑美元遭到抛售，墨西哥比索领跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexican-peso-rand-lead-em-currency-selloff-on-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税引发通胀和经济增长担忧，金属价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收关税，贸易战可能加剧全球经济增长，从铜到铁矿石等工业金属价格随之暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普考虑下一轮关税，欧洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/european-stock-futures-slide-as-trump-eyes-next-round-of-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者担心该地区将成为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普贸易关税的下一个目标，欧洲股市暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/european-stock-futures-slide-as-trump-eyes-next-round-of-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:53:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：关税导致美元上涨、股指期货下跌 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
